    "category": "java",
    "title": "Java 死锁",
    "date": "2026-04-03",
    "summary": "Coffman 条件（必须同时满足）：",
    "tags": [
      "ai"
    ],
    "group": "concurrent",
    "draft": false,
    "content": "<h1>Java 死锁</h1>\n\n<h2>一、死锁条件</h2>\n<p>Coffman 条件（必须同时满足）：</p>\n<ol>\n  <li><strong>互斥</strong>：资源一次只能被一个进程占用</li>\n  <li><strong>占有等待</strong>：持有资源的同时等待其他资源</li>\n  <li><strong>不可抢占</strong>：已分配的资源不能被强制剥夺</li>\n  <li><strong>循环等待</strong>：进程间形成循环等待链</li>\n</ol>\n\n<h2>二、死锁示例</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">public class DeadlockDemo {\n    private static final Object lockA = new Object();\n    private static final Object lockB = new Object();\n    \n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        Thread t1 = new Thread(() -> {\n            synchronized (lockA) {\n                System.out.println(\"T1: Holding lock A\");\n                sleep(100);\n                synchronized (lockB) {  // 等待 lockB\n                    System.out.println(\"T1: Holding lock B\");\n                }\n            }\n        });\n        \n        Thread t2 = new Thread(() -> {\n            synchronized (lockB) {\n                System.out.println(\"T2: Holding lock B\");\n                sleep(100);\n                synchronized (lockA) {  // 等待 lockA\n                    System.out.println(\"T2: Holding lock A\");\n                }\n            }\n        });\n        \n        t1.start();\n        t2.start();\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h2>三、死锁检测</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\"># 使用 jstack 检测\njstack -l PID | grep -A 50 \"deadlock\"\n\n# 输出示例\nFound one Java-level deadlock:\n=============================\n\"Thread-1\":\n  waiting to lock monitor 0x00007f8b4c0 (object 0x123, a java.lang.Object),\n  which is held by \"Thread-0\"\n\"Thread-0\":\n  waiting to lock monitor 0x00007f8b4d0 (object 0x456, a java.lang.Object),\n  which is held by \"Thread-1\"</code></pre>\n\n<h2>四、死锁预防</h2>\n<h3>1. 资源有序分配</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">// 按固定顺序获取锁\nprivate void safeTransfer(Account from, Account to, int amount) {\n    Account first = from.id < to.id ? from : to;\n    Account second = from.id < to.id ? to : from;\n    \n    synchronized (first) {\n        synchronized (second) {\n            // 转账操作\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3>2. 超时获取</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">if (lock.tryLock(3, TimeUnit.SECONDS)) {\n    try {\n        // 操作\n    } finally {\n        lock.unlock();\n    }\n} else {\n    // 超时处理\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h3>3. 使用并发工具类</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-java\">// 使用 ConcurrentHashMap 替代 Hashtable\n// 使用 CopyOnWriteArrayList\n// 使用阻塞队列</code></pre>\n\n<h2>五、死锁避免 - 银行家算法</h2>\n<p>动态检测资源分配状态，确保不会进入不安全状态。</p>\n\n<h2>六、死锁解除</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>进程终止</strong>：终止一个或多个死锁进程</li>\n  <li><strong>资源剥夺</strong>：强行剥夺资源分配给其他进程</li>\n</ul>\n"
